<span id="freeTextContainer13639141888935799919">I was so excited to read this book, but after the first half I couldn&apos;t read anymore. The book started out really well, but eventually I got tired of the characters. I am exhausted by these female characters that have zero self confidence, and never think they are good enough for the male lead. Even David got tiresome, after him always wanting to talk about things later. In the first half of the book, he barely revealed anything about what kind of a person he was. I can definitely see this book </span>
